{
  "stem": "10181.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he kept-- sort of as a-- as a good journalist, he kept sort of a blow by blow account of what was happening-- like an eyewitness account, you know, which is always the best because, afterwards, years later, you remember but you don't really remember the things exactly the way they were.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he made this part of a book which he published.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He published about his own hometown.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He wasn't from Dinslaken.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was from somewhere else, but this-- the chapter was devoted to the Kristallnacht in Dinslaken.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, the town of Dinslaken itself, the elders went to-- some years ago-- went to visit him in Israel and bought this-- bought this from him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, they gave him-- they wanted to because he wasn't doing well, so they gave him money for it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they published it and to show the people what-- how bad they had been, you know, and how dangerous it is to-- to-- like-- like people always say the worst part of it was people stand by and watch.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, they don't-- they don't do anything about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, they just-- they're bystanders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was the majority of people who were bystanders, and some of them were very active, you know, in-- in helping the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really, you know, because the thing is, I can't judge what happened in '33 and '34 because I was too small.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was surprised at the Kristallnacht because it had been violent, but not-- nothing-- nothing special-- you know, nothing more than had been the day before the day before the day before.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Kristallnacht was a-- it was a program.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's-- it's-- it's a fully-fledged program.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was done by the government.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a government-organized program.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
